arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start(idActorPlayer, sLevelAreaName)
	if(Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idActorPlayer)) then
		--Boss Respawn Trigger Enabled
		Hydra.ActorEnable(BOSS_TRIGGER)
	end
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	if(Hydra.ActorIsAlive(idActor)) then
		--Disable Trigger
		Hydra.ActorDisable(BOSS_TRIGGER)
		--Send Event
		Hydra.EventSend("QST_VGN_Hawe_Verge_03_ValthaBoss_Start")
	end
end
